{"tid":1654671,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[2000蚊成本]　女神像獅子山被毀　靈魂不滅守護香港","createTime":"2019-10-14T16:52:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-15T08:28:17.000Z","uid":114891,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"864fc8da18c1d487e246f74be0253d4929781daf","tid":1654671,"uid":114891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T16:52:36.000Z","msg":"佢地為香港留低左一個美好既記憶，雖然藝術品唔應該用價錢去衡量，不過除番開2000蚊成本，一切都值得。手足，多謝你。<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg10-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/72172709_1508233169315698_7496615838913396736_n.jpg?_nc_cat=102&amp;_nc_oc=AQnIavUUtgvC5JMBP0irRtqZY8EkL0TxWwTYEEGETGLUoWy2cpPEZUdl2MWX9M2rRPw&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg10-1.fna&amp;oh=0fb59781a6e808dcaadaa3b2798b9889&amp;oe=5E65305D\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg10-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F72172709_1508233169315698_7496615838913396736_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D102%26_nc_oc%3DAQnIavUUtgvC5JMBP0irRtqZY8EkL0TxWwTYEEGETGLUoWy2cpPEZUdl2MWX9M2rRPw%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg10-1.fna%26oh%3D0fb59781a6e808dcaadaa3b2798b9889%26oe%3D5E65305D&h=5df07d74&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》就事件向女神像團隊查詢，團隊表示被破壞是意料中事，認為<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">女神聳立在獅子山上的姿態已被全港人見證，無人可以破壞香港人的記憶</span></strong>。他們不推測是誰做，但指一定是害怕民主思想植入香港人意識的人，暫時無計劃修復，並認為雕像應由破壞者去清理，「破壞者覺得個像唔應該出現係獅子頭就應該付出相應努力。」<br />\n<br />\n團隊又指出，當日女神像共眾籌20萬元，材料成本約4.5萬元，多次運輸共花1萬元，另有5.5萬元預留用於日後製作小型女神像義賣，餘下的9萬元已捐予星火同盟被捕支援。<br />\n<br />\n透過眾籌所籌得的款項，主要用來製作一座四米高香港民主女神像及<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>20個一米高雕像</strong></span>，其成本包括3D打印、製作材料、印刷、物流及儲存費用等。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20191014&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=60151730\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20191014%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D60151730&d=ZEuQNtRgUz7rCGSUvjEm92mu51%2BDyw7Majob2ybULac%3D&h=5b29c7e2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20191014%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D60151730&h=6a5b47ba\" target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20191014&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=60151730</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190829/20758020\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190829%2F20758020&d=ZEuQNtRgUz7rCGSUvjEm92mu51%2BDyw7Majob2ybULac%3D&h=4db8a744\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190829%2F20758020&h=19625953\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190829/20758020</a>"},{"pid":"d291d45488536b791c1981085c23be8c259bf85f","tid":1654671,"uid":118120,"like":2,"dislike":7,"score":-5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T16:54:08.000Z","msg":"點會有呢d 安排, 拎完上去就應該拎返落黎啦<br />\n就咁擺o係度藍絲唔搞你先奇<br />\n係嫌錢多定係點 ?"},{"pid":"665eff7b27703a645ec275001d125d389e9b9762","tid":1654671,"uid":114891,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T16:54:16.000Z","msg":"藍絲今日打爛既只係一件物件<br />\n而女神像背後既民主理念<br />\n係打唔爛架<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;Behind this mask there is more than just flesh. Beneath this mask there is an idea... and ideas are bulletproof.&rdquo;"},{"pid":"757802e09aa214ead9308958da6857a76522f0a0","tid":1654671,"uid":245127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T16:54:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">推</span><br />\n- <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">屌你老母 今晚儲夠人 今日美國傾 <br />\n但twitter 熱門一個香港都冇 </span></span> <br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n全部人：國際線啊！！！！幾個製出個tweet 有幾難啊<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1654565\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1654565</a> </span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</span